sections.heading: to 69-20-21 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1987, ch. 234, § 84 repealed 69-20-1 to 69-20-21 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1933, ch. 153, §§ 122, 123, 125, 126, 128, 130 to 133, 138, 140, 141, relating to ventilation of gases in coal mines, effective July 1, 1987. For present comparable provisions,see69-8-1 to 69-8-15 NMSA 1978.
